column5: Anyone been to Deer Horn lodge on the Cabonga Res. this year? If you have, how were things? Anything we should know? Leaving soon, can't wait.

Just got back from DHL this Saturday and it was awesome. Best fishing in years! Lake was down about 3 feet when we got there and it looks like it lost another foot during the week. Caught a five pound Walleye in Baie Mike! Lost a trophy pike in 5 mile Baie by the boat, but ####, I already have a trophy pike that I caught in 1980, 33 Lbs and 44 inches. Let me know how you do!
